<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_321_r2l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als eẅr <expan>durchlewchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft an vns <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l3">hat / aber von meͣr vnd lewff <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von Beheim herauſʒ etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l4">Alſo tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ vns ein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l7">nechten ſpat geſagt vnd ſchrıft geweıſet hat 
<add><ab facs="#facs_321_line_1577277176659_648">die Jm <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey von </ab><ab facs="#facs_321_line_1577277178398_653"><expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_321_line_1577277179953_658">guten </ab><ab facs="#facs_321_line_1577277182033_663">freẅnd </ab></add> wıe es auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l10">dem perg <expan>ʒun<ex>n</ex></expan> Chutten <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_321_r2l9">vnd beteydıngt </ab></add> ſol ſeın / <expan>Derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſchrıft wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l12"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> hıerynn <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_321_r2l13">wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
