</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ewr
                            <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift an uns
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat, aber von meͣr und lewff
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> von Beheim herausz etc., also tun wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        uns ein <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> auf nechten spat gesagt und schrift geweiset
                        hat, <add>die im <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey von
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> guten frewnd</add>, wie es auf dem
                        Perg <expan>zun<ex>n</ex></expan> Chutten <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>und beteydingt</add> sol sein, <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> schrift
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> hierynn <expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                    <add><expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>i,</ex></expan></add>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>exalta<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
<expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
